    <briefdescription>
<para>Task-level watchdog monitor. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each registered task must &quot;check in&quot; periodically. If any task misses its deadline, the watchdog fires a callback (typically system reset).</para>
<para>This is distinct from a hardware watchdog — it monitors individual software tasks, not just the main loop.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structSYN__Watchdog" kindref="compound">SYN_Watchdog</ref><sp/>wdt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structSYN__WDT__Entry" kindref="compound">SYN_WDT_Entry</ref><sp/>entries[3];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="syn__watchdog_8c_1a3ac9a3ed9c1aaa8ae7c9e33c60d7a55e" kindref="member">syn_watchdog_init</ref>(&amp;wdt,<sp/>entries,<sp/>3,<sp/>on_timeout,<sp/>NULL);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>id0<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="syn__watchdog_8c_1ad3f59b704a8bbfe504f174a88a72eb1c" kindref="member">syn_watchdog_register</ref>(&amp;wdt,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;sensor&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>5000);<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>5s<sp/>timeout</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>id1<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="syn__watchdog_8c_1ad3f59b704a8bbfe504f174a88a72eb1c" kindref="member">syn_watchdog_register</ref>(&amp;wdt,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;comms&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/><sp/>2000);</highlight></codeline>
